\insrsid489342\charrsid6557717  Cullis have to do, she just came on the Tuesday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Yes. She - she had different days, to - different houses to go, and - as my grandmother, in her time with two - children dependant, so Mrs}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086728\charrsid6557717 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717  Cullis - was going from house to house different days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 What did you call her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Mrs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086728\charrsid6557717 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 
 Cullis, we - and I can remember another woman that used to come periodically. She 
was - a dressmaker from Manwr Buchan, and - one of the conditions of her coming that I being a strong youngster was going down to carry the Singer machine. And it was a - about a mile, about a mile coming up from there, and I can always remember - that Mi
r
iam - Miriam - Jenkins, by name, she would - maybe be there for - a week or a fortnight, until we had all been rigged out with a new - flannel shirts, and - cutting the clothes down for the oldest ones for the younger ones and make do it was in that time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Did your mother make any of your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Would she mend any of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Oh no, always mending.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 What about your father, would he make or mend any clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 No, he wasn't that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Would you have new clothes or secondhand clothes, you did mention that you had them cut down from the oldest to the youngest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 
Yes, I would be having - some of the - of the clothes - that were coming, they would come after my uncle's - some such jacket or something, that would be cut down
. The other thing my - my father was a very keen gardener. In the old - Tetocown, there wax - an extensive garden. And - he was known as the first one who experimented with - budding roses on to a dog rose stoc}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12086728\charrsid6557717 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 . And I can remember - the joy that he used t
o show his friends how he had budded a rose called - Dorothy Pdrkins onto this dog rose. Then came the war in 1914. And - the allotment craze started, and he was a very keen man with the allotment association.
