 due - if possible - to coincide with Whitsun. Whitsun. The turn out of the Sunday school was - but there was another consideration as far as we boys were concerned, it had to coincide with - the quarter ending of the Co-operative. There would be - quite 
a
 lot of saving - to clear the quarter, clear what was due for the quarter, and then after the beginning of the quarter, if anybody had to have new boots, or new - clothes of any kind, my mother used to say, well you'll have to wait - until after Pencwarte
r Co-op, which was the quarter ending.
