ho did suffer - bilious attacks periodically - I would volunteer very often to scrub out. On condition that the doors were closed and nobody were coming in, I'd scrub from the front door we had tiles from the front door, into through a passage leading thr
ough to the kitchen, and then I would do the flags afterwards with a scrubbing brush I would - scrub out from the front door to the back door - if my mother had a bilious - but - that would be - I wasn't - wanting that to be a regular course.
