\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 It wouldn't be the minister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 No, not the minister, at - at that, it was one of the deacons that would take us in that meeting.
