\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Yes, you'd have a kind of squawk now and then but - nobody used to take any - any notice. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Did you have different clothes?
