Yes. All the Sunday clothes were different - and - smelling of camphor and - put away as soon as Sunday was over, and - wouldn't be looked at until the following Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Did you play games?
