Yes, every game that went. And on - and on - cat and dog. And we'd have marbles in season. And if it came to a moonlight night, we would have a game - fox and hounds, where one would be chosen to be the fox and all the other pack would
 be after him, 'til they found where he was, and - that was the favourite on - on a moonlight night. Football, we had football in school - and - played rugby - from ten, from ten 'til we left school. Plenty of - of that kind of thing.
