\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15352313 JE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 Not very, you were down to Neath - four miles down to Neath, then you'd go on to - Skewan, Morriston, oh we -
