Oh yes. We - in - I can remember in my grandmother's house - there were no activities at all, even the vegetables had been cleaned and ready, and the meat cooked on the Saturday. And I've heard my 
mother saying she was the eldest of the children, of the girls in that household, and first thing on Monday morning you'd have the accumulation of all those dishes - and she would - that was her job first thing on Monday morning.
