here are - the prize would be - a guineas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5178564\charrsid6557717  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 
