A few of them. A few of them, she would - either there the - my sister, the eldest sister would have to just look after the children, and the younger ones only that they were at home, and - my mother wouldn't lose - the - if there 
was an invited speaker - for the - literary society. She would always see to go to those. And - of course at that time you had the temperance - movement, the Good Templars, and - the missionary meetings. Those were the meetings that my mother would always
 -
