Sometime yes, I - I would - the only regret I have got now - but I have acquired - a taste for - literature, for books and so forth, but in - I never was able to write - to my s
atisfaction, and never to be able to write correctly. The regrets I had I - I am asked, I think that - I have an ability to express myself, verbally. But I could not do that - writing, as I never - I don't even know today - what - various terms - mean. An
d - I know by looking at a word that it's wrong, that it's - ill spelt, but I couldn't prove - were it is wrong.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14483652 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 You had no lessons at all in school on grammar?
