ut there we knew how to read, we knew how to write, and - we used to have periodical visitors, who - used to - lecture to us. I can well remember - the time when - decline we used to call it in - in welsh, consumption was rampant, I can remember many of t
h
e - children in school just wasting away and - we would bring our pennies to get a wreath, they had died of consumption. Well then we would have somebody to come and - and give a lecture or give a talk - on - consumption, and then we would have to - write
 
a composition the following day on what we heard. Well during the - during the lecture, the - speaker had said about - the advantage of eat - eating - fresh vegetables. And - he mentioned - that - the - lettuce, lettuce was very very good for our health, 
and that they - they were composed of the drug }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6450268\charrsid6557717 laudanum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 
, and that it was a good thing to - grow these. And to grow them early and - protect them - with a sheet of tarpaulin. But the following day writing the essay, I said that the drug that came from lettuc
