\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid949540\charrsid6557717 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid489342\charrsid6557717 
man gardener, and I was there until 1935, when the - 1935 - job was - advertised in Bridgend Grammar School for a gardener ground}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid949540\charrsid6557717 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
